00:00:28.520 --> 00:00:49.520
I want to talk to you just real quick about what we tell our players.

00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:55.520
I think it will help everybody here on the show.

00:00:55.520 --> 00:01:00.520
Now obviously we all go through adverse situations.

00:01:00.520 --> 00:01:04.520
Be it something major that happens to your family or to you or something minor.

00:01:04.520 --> 00:01:07.520
Find out a friend's lying to you or something like that.

00:01:07.520 --> 00:01:11.520
We all deal with it differently.

00:01:11.520 --> 00:01:18.520
But we say to some of our players, we ask them consistently to play their next play.

00:01:18.520 --> 00:01:22.520
Don't get caught up in the play that just happened.

00:01:22.520 --> 00:01:25.520
Play the next play.

00:01:25.520 --> 00:01:28.520
And if you think about the quiet edge of your life,

00:01:28.520 --> 00:01:32.520
don't get caught up in the things that are behind you or the things that are in front of you.

00:01:32.520 --> 00:01:34.520
Just go play the next play.

00:01:34.520 --> 00:01:38.520
And I think it will really help you with the things that you are attempting to do.

00:01:38.520 --> 00:01:41.520
Be it sports, school, whatever it is.

00:01:41.520 --> 00:01:44.520
I've got a quick little analogy for you.

00:01:44.520 --> 00:01:49.520
